$ System.Net.HttpWebRequest (class)

`System.Net.HttpWebRequest` derives from → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Net/WebRequest[`WebRequest`] (as also does
→ Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Net/FtpWebRequest[`System.Net.FtpWebRequest`]).

→ Microsoft recommends to use `System.Net.Http.HttpClient` instead of `System.Net.HttpWebRequest`.

sa:
  Proxy settings are controlled through → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Net/WebProxy[`System.Net.WebProxy`]
